data.title: Webster Groves School District
data.text:
The Webster Groves School District, which has served the community for over 150 years, is looking for a superintendent who can build on its legacy of educational excellence. The district serves approximately 4,300 students and is supported by a dedicated staff of nearly 730 employees across nine schools.

Dr. Simpson intends to retire at the end of the 2024-25 school year, after serving nearly three decades in public education, including the last 9 years as WGSD superintendent.
